Package com.example.duckduckgoose.waitlist

Class WaitlistEntry

java.lang.Object
com.example.duckduckgoose.waitlist.WaitlistEntry
public class WaitlistEntry extends Object
Represents an entry in the waitlist collection, tracking the relationship between users and events. Each entry maintains the user's status in relation to a specific event's waitlist, including timestamps for when they joined and when they were accepted (if applicable).
